A cyberpunk-style scene showing a holographic interview table in a neon-lit tech lab, where translucent data streams and code fragments float in mid-air between two empty futuristic chairs. The environment features dark metallic surfaces with cyan and magenta accent lighting, circuit board patterns embedded in glass walls, and floating geometric shapes representing different programming concepts orbiting the space like satellites. Rain streaks down floor-to-ceiling windows revealing a sprawling megacity skyline beyond. The atmosphere conveys evaluation, potential, and the merging of human connection with technical mastery.
